So, one day he said, ‘We can’t turn it in,

00:22:56.112 --> 00:22:58.281
but let’s try filling out
a marriage registration form."

00:22:58.348 --> 00:22:59.282
HUSBAND-TO-BE: SAKU SAKUTA

00:22:59.349 --> 00:23:02.953
But after we wrote it,

00:23:03.019 --> 00:23:05.555
