Well, answer me.

00:26:29.659 --> 00:26:34.297
Look, you wouldn't normally ask
other people that, would you?

00:26:34.898 --> 00:26:37.934
It's not good manners to ask questions
you wouldn't normally ask people.

00:26:40.670 --> 00:26:43.239
But this is my first time
meeting someone like that.

00:26:43.740 --> 00:26:45.375
It's probably not your first.

00:26:46.176 --> 00:26:48.812
They say there's about one or two
in every 100 people.

00:26:49.379 --> 00:26:51.147
I’m sure there are some
at your school too.

00:26:52.148 --> 00:26:54.651
You just don’t see them.

00:26:58.722 --> 00:26:59.823
FAMILY PACK ICE CREAM

00:26:59.889 --> 00:27:01.858
Want something?

00:27:03.660 --> 00:27:04.694
Since we’re here,

00:27:05.261 --> 00:27:06.496
pick whatever you like.

00:27:09.432 --> 00:27:11.167
-Then I'll have this.
