00:27:12.669 --> 00:27:14.571
Oh, this one doesn't come with a discount.

00:27:15.872 --> 00:27:17.340
A hair swirl!

00:27:18.408 --> 00:27:19.843
What?

00:27:19.909 --> 00:27:22.779
Something you don’t notice,
but it’s there.

00:27:24.347 --> 00:27:25.215
Hair swirl, huh?

00:27:26.850 --> 00:27:27.851
Sorry.

00:27:29.385 --> 00:27:31.154
For what?

00:27:31.221 --> 00:27:34.324
The other day, I hated it
when you assumed I had parents.

00:27:34.390 --> 00:27:36.025
But I said something similar to you.

00:27:37.627 --> 00:27:39.763
Wait. You don't have parents?

00:27:39.829 --> 00:27:40.663
No.

00:27:42.932 --> 00:27:45.769
But the person you were with earlier…

00:27:45.835 --> 00:27:47.370
That was my former dad.

00:27:47.437 --> 00:27:49.839
My parents divorced. He has a new family.

00:27:49.906 --> 00:27:52.509
My mom… Well, a lot happened.

00:27:54.110 --> 00:27:57.080
I’m sorry for assuming.

00:27:58.615 --> 00:27:59.783
Is being gay hard?

00:27:59.849 --> 00:28:00.717
Huh?

00:28:04.654 --> 00:28:06.122
What about you?

00:28:06.189 --> 00:28:07.557
Then, are you glad you’re gay?

00:28:10.794 --> 00:28:14.464
I want to believe I am.

00:28:15.565 --> 00:28:16.833
So, what do you do?

00:28:18.001 --> 00:28:18.868
What do you mean?

00:28:19.369 --> 00:28:21.271
How do you come
to feel good about being gay?

00:28:28.144 --> 00:28:29.612
Love and revolution?

00:28:36.052 --> 00:28:37.120
Good afternoon.

00:28:38.288 --> 00:28:40.790
So, you’re here today to complete
your membership paperwork?

00:28:40.857 --> 00:28:44.093
