a marriage registration form?

00:29:04.047 --> 00:29:07.317
Have you heard of the term "family glue"?

00:29:07.383 --> 00:29:09.352
Like, "Children bring
the family together?"

00:29:09.419 --> 00:29:12.889
I think couples who last a long time
have something like that.

00:29:12.956 --> 00:29:16.993
It's hard to sustain it
based only on love or affection.

00:29:18.228 --> 00:29:19.262
The "glue"…

00:29:19.963 --> 00:29:23.466
-Well then, please fill out this form--
-Thank you.

00:29:25.068 --> 00:29:26.536
Thank you.

